{"tid":1565670,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[光復香港]觀塘中秋放映會，今晚見！","createTime":"2019-09-13T08:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T13:08:21.000Z","uid":85574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e4ce837b88328c3006f2e38ba27816a47503ca5","tid":1565670,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:47:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">觀塘中秋放映會</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚10點到會同班朋友係觀塘D出口附近搞放映會，播2014年烏克蘭的抗爭記錄片 -Winter On Fire<br />\n<br />\n唔知會唔會有機會同其他手足撞機，撞左就睇下附近搵個位再Set機擺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唱完國歌同食完中秋飯可以過黎睇下！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">到時見！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7a218c0a9343df978e3f0febc4a3f2d38c9ddd53","tid":1565670,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:47:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=7e9a75f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"a655c69840573dc494682e85a0789783c5ec87b4","tid":1565670,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"a7292425404b93edf157b31660a6fc40aaf99370","tid":1565670,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d310469454f45f8daefad2584c50cd189f287fb9","tid":1565670,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:48:23.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"f2cc25d95b926e73ac247b5353a5825061d4045b","tid":1565670,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"2a21fb863283bbe255da8fb90ea3f7349687e94f","tid":1565670,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:48:44.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"5351c649b5fcdfb42abd21a6168f43dcc9813498","tid":1565670,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:48:57.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"659caaf217e783bdfaece82a4c6bb8a36ad4f3b7","tid":1565670,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"789fb75ed0b14f5b60400a4ec912f098f7734ab5","tid":1565670,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:49:21.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"e5d7a5262a70350aaf8f59e014ff34acff207323","tid":1565670,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:49:31.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"68b89080729c8fc23d5288c10de88d742f5e3fef","tid":1565670,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"b6c8ef45626560e58276369bb8650e2